T01H
First Place Winner!
2012 Chicago IGDA Game Jam

by Team ADHD:

Scott Walenty - programmer
Kyle Jenkins - background/environment artist
Dave Fulton - character artist/animator
James Becker - programmer
Thomas Field - level designer

Sound and music done by Andrew Mortega

Written in C# / XNA 4.0

Entire game designed and implemented in less than 39 hours.

Theme: "The Goal is to Lose"

Premise:
A robot trucker is on his ship, named T01H, and suddenly the ship malfunctions and is headed directly for a robot orphanage. Can he prevent this possible disaster?